[FILE:197:files/pkg-message-single.in]
Before using EDE make sure that "/etc/machine-id" exists. If it doesn't, 
generate it with:
	dbus-uuidgen > /etc/machine-id

To start EDE via startx, put "exec startede" into your ~/.xinitrc file.

